# 💥 Why drain gets stuck

Very common reasons:

### 1. Pod cannot be evicted

* PDB (PodDisruptionBudget)
* Static pod
* DaemonSet (normally ignored, but sometimes blocks)

### 2. Control plane node

You are draining a **master node**, so:

* etcd / apiserver / controller pods exist
* eviction is sensitive

